  <brief_title>Comparing Two Types of Sedation to Gynaecological Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Deep Sedation in Spontaneously Breathing Patients Combined With Local Anesthesia Versus General Anesthesia in Gynecological Patients at Same Day Surgical at Hospitalsenheden Horsens</official_title>
